  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  one ulcerative lesion ≤ 900 mm2 in total area,

          -  ≥ 12 years,

          -  parasitologically diagnosed by visualization of amastigotes or culture of
             promastigotes from lesion material,

          -  no antileishmanial therapy in the last 3 months,

          -  no mucosal lesions,

          -  no history of significant concomitant diseases including immunosuppression.

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
